  "keyFeatures": [
    "20+ pre-built plugins for different job functions",
    "Skills that provide automatic domain expertise",
    "Slash commands for explicit workflows",
    "MCP connector integration for external tools",
    "File-based customization with no code required",
    "Support for both Claude Cowork and Claude Code",
    "Plugin management tools for creating custom plugins",
    "Extensive connector ecosystem (CRM, project management, data warehouses, etc.)"
